  "about": [
    "Bogdanov is often called the \"Siberian hermit,\" because he rarely leaves the remote town of Surgut and avoids public attention.",
    "His Surgutneftegas managed to accumulate a huge cash pile of $56 billion at 2021, much more than the company's market capitalization."
